      *              * le                                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-num-mcp-wme    not  < w-det-num-mcp-wmf and
                     w-det-num-mcp-wsa    =    w-det-num-mcp-waf
                     go to det-num-mcp-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se mese da escludere                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-num-mcp-mde    not  = zero and
                     w-det-num-mcp-wme    =    w-det-num-mcp-mde
                     go to det-num-mcp-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Incremento numero mesi                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-det-num-mcp-nme      .
